race.description: Tas Breeders Life Member Jenny Watson Hcp (C1)
race.comment: MAZZINI (2) was backed off the map leading and winning by 7.5L on the Devonport synthetic on debut. Had come off easy trial wins there and at Longford and resumes today with a Longford trial win under the saddle. He's sure to have come on and should take a stack of beating. DAYTONA DIVA (6) resumes off a comfortable win at Hobart on debut. Won a recent Longford trial easily and maps well. Should be right in it. HALEN (1) was third up and improved sharply here winning his Maiden. Has a handy 2kg claim today and can get into the money. Races forward and can make the finish. SNOW MAIDEN (3) is another last start Maiden winner who will be around the mark with an in-form jockey sticking.
